org.gradoop.common.model.api.entities

Interface GraphElement

  • All Superinterfaces:
    Attributed, Element, Identifiable, Labeled, Serializable
    All Known Subinterfaces:
    Edge, Vertex
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    EPGMEdge, EPGMGraphElement, EPGMVertex

    public interface GraphElement
extends Element
    A graph element is part of a graph. An element can be part of more than one graph. This applies to vertices and edges.
